---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout theme="welcome" activeSlug="welcome" title="Phone That Cares About You">
  <article class="welcome">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>

    <div class="body-text" data-nav-fade-trigger>
      <p>
        Hey there. My name is Brian, and this website is a home for a
        speculative design project I've been working on, which I've called
        A Phone That Cares About You.
      </p>
      <p>
        In brief: I think the first person who makes a phone you can buy —
        one that actively helps you navigate both the internet and your
        intentions for interacting with it — will probably shift the default
        for all mobile devices and change the way the internet works in
        general.
      </p>
      <p>
        I don't know that I'll be the one to make a billion dollars from
        this, but I'm trying to help it happen faster, more beautifully.
      </p>
      <p>On this website you'll find:</p>
      <ul class="site-contents">
        <li><a href="/vision">Next steps</a> for what a business built around better phones could look like</li>
        <li>Particular UI concepts and <a href="/experiments">experiments</a></li>
        <li><a href="/thinking">Visuals</a>, doodles, and infographics explaining my thinking</li>
        <li><a href="/writing">Essays</a> on the economic and business models behind phone manufacturers</li>
        <li>Opportunities to <a href="/collaborate">collaborate</a>, reach out, and give feedback</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <footer class="contact">
      <p>
        Interested? Get in touch:
        <a href="mailto:anothernotherbrian@gmail.com">anothernotherbrian@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .welcome {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .welcome h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .body-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .body-text p {
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .site-contents {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .site-contents li {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.8vw, 1.05rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .contact {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .contact p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
